      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/crypto-whales-get-nod-from-eric-trump-that-party-s-just-starting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在阿布扎比举行的比特币会议上，埃里克·特朗普站在挤满人的人群面前，准备向那些已经皈依加密货币的人宣传加密货币。他分享了一条令人欣喜的消息：他的父亲、当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将把美国变成“世界加密货币之都”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/crypto-whales-get-nod-from-eric-trump-that-party-s-just-starting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 12:50:54 GMT</pubDate>
